===儿童性虐待===
儿童性侵犯通常被认为比成年人性侵犯更加恶劣。这是因为儿童受害人是天真无辜的，也是因为侵犯对儿童所造成的心理负面影响时间更长。

儿童性侵犯是虐待儿童的一种形式，成人或年纪较大的未成年人会虐待儿童，作为性发泄对象。<ref name=medline2008>{{cite web |url=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/childsexualabuse.html |title=Child Sexual Abuse |work=Medline Plus |date=2008-04-02 |publisher=U.S. National Library of Medicine, |accessdate=2014-10-01 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225045055/https://medlineplus.gov/childsexualabuse.html%20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="APA Guidelines">{{cite journal |doi=10.1037/0003-066X.54.8.586 |laysummary=http://psycnet.apa.org/index.cfm?fa=buy.optionToBuy&uid=1999-03403-007 |laysource=APA PsycNET |laydate=2008-05-07 |quote='''Abuse, sexual (child)''': generally defined as contacts between a child and an adult or other person significantly older or in a position of power or control over the child, where the child is being used for sexual stimulation of the adult or other person |title=Guidelines for psychological evaluations in child protection matters |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-psychologist_1999-08_54_8/page/586 |year=1999 |journal=American Psychologist |volume=54 |issue=8 |pages=586–93 |pmid=10453704}}</ref>儿童性侵犯的形式包括要求或逼迫儿童参与性活动(无论结果如何)，将生殖器官以不恰当的方式暴露给孩子看，给他们看色情片，与儿童发生性关系，物理接触儿童的性器官，在没有接触的情况下观看儿童的性器官，使用儿童制作色情片。<ref name=medline2008/><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/0145-2134(93)90061-9 |title=Asking about child sexual abuse: Methodological implications of a two stage survey |year=1993 |last1=Martin |first1=Judy |last2=Anderson |first2=Jessie |last3=Romans |first3=Sarah |last4=Mullen |first4=Paul |last5=O'Shea |first5=Martine |journal=Child Abuse & Neglect |volume=17 |issue=3 |pages=383–92 |pmid=8330225}}</ref><ref name=nspcc>{{cite web |url=http://www.nspcc.org.uk/help-and-advice/worried-about-a-child/online-advice/sexual-abuse/sexual-abuse-a_wda87108.html |title=Child sexual abuse definition from |publisher=the NSPCC |accessdate=2011-12-09 |archive-date=2012-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207170534/http://www.nspcc.org.uk/help-and-advice/worried-about-a-child/online-advice/sexual-abuse/sexual-abuse-a_wda87108.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

儿童性侵犯的后果包括[[抑郁|抑郁]]、<ref name="Roosa">{{cite journal |pmid=10197407 |year=1999 |last1=Roosa |first1=MW |last2=Reinholtz |first2=C |last3=Angelini |first3=PJ |title=The relation of child sexual abuse and depression in young women: Comparisons across four ethnic groups |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-abnormal-child-psychology_1999-02_27_1/page/65 |volume=27 |issue=1 |pages=65–76 |journal=Journal of abnormal child psychology}}</ref>[[创伤后心理压力紧张综合症|创伤后心理压力紧张综合症]]、<ref name="widom">{{cite journal |pmid=10450264 |year=1999 |last1=Widom |first1=CS |title=Posttraumatic stress disorder in abused and neglected children grown up |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-psychiatry_1999-08_156_8/page/1223 |volume=156 |issue=8 |pages=1223–9 |journal=The American journal of psychiatry}}</ref>[[焦虑|焦虑]]、<ref name="levitan">{{cite journal |doi=10.1002/da.10077 |title=Childhood adversities associated with major depression and/or anxiety disorders in a community sample of Ontario: Issues of co-morbidity and specificity |year=2003 |last1=Levitan |first1=Robert D. |last2=Rector |first2=Neil A. |last3=Sheldon |first3=Tess |last4=Goering |first4=Paula |journal=Depression and Anxiety |volume=17 |pages=34–42 |pmid=12577276 |issue=1}}</ref>在成人期时容易再次成为受害人、<ref name="Messman-Moore">{{cite journal |doi=10.1177/088626000015005003 |title=Child Sexual Abuse and Revictimization in the Form of Adult Sexual Abuse, Adult Physical Abuse, and Adult Psychological Maltreatment |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-interpersonal-violence_2000-05_15_5/page/489 |year=2000 |last1=Messman-Moore |first1=T. L. |last2=Long |first2=P. J. |journal=Journal of Interpersonal Violence |volume=15 |issue=5 |pages=489–502}}</ref>对儿童造成物理伤害等其它问题。<ref name="dinw">{{cite journal |doi=10.1017/S0033291799001373 |title=Early sexual abuse and lifetime psychopathology: A co-twin–control study |year=2000 |last1=Dinwiddie |first1=S. |last2=Heath |first2=A. C. |last3=Dunne |first3=M. P. |last4=Bucholz |first4=K. K. |last5=Madden |first5=P. A. F. |last6=Slutske |first6=W. S. |last7=Bierut |first7=L. J. |last8=Statham |first8=D. B. |last9=Martin |first9=N. G. |displayauthors=9 <!--exactly 9 authors--> |journal=Psychological Medicine |volume=30 |pages=41–52 |pmid=10722174 |issue=1}}</ref>家庭成员实施的儿童性虐待是一种乱伦行为，是儿童性侵犯中最常见的形式，后果更加恶劣，造成长期心理创伤，特别是当家长乱伦的时候。<ref name=Courtois>{{cite book|title=Healing the Incest Wound: Adult Survivors in Therapy|url=https://archive.org/details/healingincestwou00cour|last= Courtois|first=Christine A.|publisher=W. W. Norton & Company|page=[https://archive.org/details/healingincestwou00cour/page/208 208]|year=1988|isbn= 0-393-31356-5}}</ref>

大约有15%到25%的妇女和5%到15%的男士在童年时受到性虐待。<ref name=Whealin>{{cite web |url=http://www.ptsd.va.gov/public/pages/child-sexual-abuse.asp |title=Child Sexual Abuse |author=Julia Whealin, Ph.D. |publisher=National Center for Post Traumatic Stress Disorder, US Department of Veterans Affairs |date=2007-05-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090730101002/http://www.ptsd.va.gov/public/pages/child-sexual-abuse.asp |archivedate=2009-07-30 }}</ref><ref name="Finkelhor1994">{{cite journal |author=David Finkelhor |title=Current Information on the Scope and Nature of Child Sexual Abuse |journal=The Future of Children |date=summer/fall 1994 |volume=(1994) 4(2): 31-53 |url=http://www.unh.edu/ccrc/pdf/VS75.pdf |format=PDF |access-date=2014-10-01 |archive-date=2008-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013192224/http://www.unh.edu/ccrc/pdf/VS75.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://cola.unh.edu/ccrc |title=Crimes against Children Research Center |publisher=Unh.edu |accessdate=2011-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823182214/http://cola.unh.edu/ccrc |archive-date=2013-08-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.unh.edu/frl/ |title=Family Research Laboratory |publisher=Unh.edu |accessdate=2011-12-09 |archive-date=2011-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111126193730/http://www.unh.edu/frl/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Kevin M. Gorey and Donald R. Leslie 1997 pp391–398">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/S0145-2134(96)00180-9 |title=The prevalence of child sexual abuse: Integrative review adjustment for potential response and measurement biases |year=1997 |last1=Gorey |first1=Kevin M. |last2=Leslie |first2=Donald R. |journal=Child Abuse & Neglect |volume=21 |issue=4 |pages=391–8 |pmid=9134267}}</ref>大多数施虐者熟知他们的受害人；约30%的施虐者是儿童的亲属，大多数是兄长、父母亲、姐妹、叔叔或表亲；约60%是其它熟人，如朋友、保姆、邻居；陌生人占儿童性侵犯的约10%。<ref name=Whealin/>

研究显示，当父母因乱伦而对儿童实施性侵犯时，会造成极其严重的心理伤害。<ref name="Courtois" />在儿童、未成年人、成人之间的乱伦被证实为儿童性侵犯最常见的形式，对儿童的伤害也最大。<ref name="Courtois"/>通常，儿童性虐待没有得到及时汇报有几点原因：

*儿童过于年轻，无法用语言描述受害情况
*他们被施虐者恐吓或收买贿赂
*他们因恐惧而受到注意而感到困惑
*他们害怕不被人相信
*他们感到自责，或认为虐待是一种惩罚
*他们为施虐者的后果感到内疚<ref name="pcar.org"/>

===老年性侵犯===
{{Main|虐待老人}}
老年人性侵犯是指对年过六旬的人进行性侵犯，他们大多数身体功能下降、虚弱、需要依赖他人赡养。年过65岁的受害人中只有30%向警方报案。大多数施虐者是赡养人、成年子孙、配偶或其它居住同伴。

老年人受到性侵犯的征兆有阴部撕裂、出血、瘀伤、感染、骨盆受伤、软组织和骨骼损伤。同样，情绪反复无常也是性侵犯的征兆。这些征兆包括异常激动、[[创伤后心理压力紧张综合症|创伤后心理压力紧张综合症]]、回避、恐惧、性病、已有病情恶化、失眠、恢复时间过长等。<ref name="pcar.org"/>

===性骚扰===
{{Main|性骚扰}}
性骚扰是性行为中的恐吓、虐待或胁迫，或以不受欢迎或不合适地许诺奖赏来换取性好处。<ref>{{cite book | last = Paludi | first = Michele Antoinette | authorlink = |author2=Barickman,  | title = Academic and Workplace Sexual Harassment | publisher = SUNY Press | year = 1991 | location = | pages = 2–5 | url = | doi = | id = | isbn = 0-7914-0829-9 }}</ref>在美国，性骚扰是歧视形式，触犯了《1964年民权法案》第七款。法律和社会对性骚扰的定义因文化的不同而不同。性骚扰包括大量普遍的行为，包括看似温和的冒犯到严重的虐待形式，以及其它与性侵犯像重合的形式。<ref>Dziech et al. 1990, Boland 2002</ref>性骚扰可能包括偷窥、强行约会、色情电话、袭胸、吹口哨、砸吧嘴、性歧视、播放色情材料、黄笑话、不当搂抱、对他人肢体进行评论、推荐性服务。<ref name="pcar.org">Pennsylvania Coalition Against Rape http://www.pcar.org/about-sexual-violence/stats?cat=Child+Sexual+Abuse {{Wayback|url=http://www.pcar.org/about-sexual-violence/stats?cat=Child+Sexual+Abuse |date=20141020184952 }}</ref>

===色狼===
{{Main|色狼}}
词汇色狼是指以性为目的，未经他人允许用手对他人进行触碰、抚摸(包括透过衣物)。

===家庭暴力===
{{Main|家庭暴力}}
家庭暴力是一种暴力恐吓犯罪。它与性侵犯高度相关。虐待不单单是心理的、物理的、感情的或财物的，而且也可以是性的。有的性虐待征兆与家庭暴力十分类似。{{citation needed|date=August 2012}}

===近親性侵犯===
*依據[[中華民國|中華民國]][[行政院|行政院]]發布的《國情通報》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.stat.gov.tw/ct.asp?xItem=5991&ctNode=1831&mp=4 |title=性侵害案件概況 |access-date=2014-11-29 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116032914/https://www.stat.gov.tw/ct.asp?xItem=5991&ctNode=1831&mp=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>中顯示，2003年全年度至2004年6月臺灣的[[性侵害|性侵害]]案件中，近親性侵犯（親戚與家屬）約佔7.24%；然而按照[[勵馨基金會|勵馨基金會]]的資料指出，有約近50%的性侵害受害者是近親性侵導致的，顯示在臺灣的近親性侵害受害者因為受到壓力不敢報案的的比率約5到8倍間（即黑案）；65%的近親性侵犯受害者，第一次被性侵犯的年齡在12歲以下。

*根據[[中華民國內政部|中華民國]][[內政部家庭暴力及性侵害防治委員會|衛生福利部]]的公開資訊<ref>{{Cite web|title=5.2-01 性侵害事件通報案件統計|url=https://dep.mohw.gov.tw/DOS/cp-1721-9448-113.html|work=統計處|date=2016-08-04|accessdate=2019-03-16|last=統計處|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118161835/https://dep.mohw.gov.tw/DOS/cp-1721-9448-113.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>：
**2010年度性侵害案件中，兩造關係（加害與被害者）為直系血親者約為940人左右；旁系親屬約610人左右，到2017年時，直系親屬為663人，旁系親屬則為541人。可見關係密切的家人近親性侵犯機率相當大；另，從統計表中可以看出，女性對男童近親性侵犯（如母親、阿姨、姑姑）有增加趨勢，與一般認知中的女性為受害者居多漸漸不同{{citation needed}}。（註：臺灣所指的「性侵害」，已經包含了廣義的[[性犯罪|性犯罪]]，非僅為強制性交而已。）

==心理影响==
除了明显的物理创伤之外，强奸、性侵犯创伤情况还包括对所有受害人所造成的长期心理创伤，并不局限于儿童。这些创伤包括：拒绝承认、无助、对性产生反感、[[愤怒|愤怒]]自责、[[焦虑|焦虑]]、噩梦、恐惧、抑郁、痛苦重现、[[羞耻|羞耻]]、[[合理化|找借口]]、情绪失常、木讷、淫乱、孤独、社交焦虑、信任缺失、精力不集中。成为性侵犯的受害人可能导致[[创伤后心理压力紧张综合症|创伤后心理压力紧张综合症]]、[[成瘾|成瘾]]、[[重性抑郁障碍|重性抑郁障碍]]或产生其它[[精神病理学|精神病]]。
家庭和朋友承受的心理创伤包括强烈的复仇愿望，希望能“修复”问题或是度过难关，借口以“这并不算坏事啊。”<ref name="pcar.org"/>

==预防==
性骚扰和侵犯可以通过中学<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1080/10538712.2011.622355 |title=A Sexual Assault Primary Prevention Model with Diverse Urban Youth |year=2011 |last1=Smothers |first1=Melissa Kraemer |last2=Smothers |first2=D. Brian |journal=Journal of Child Sexual Abuse |volume=20 |issue=6 |pages=708–27 |pmid=22126112}}</ref>大学<ref name=Foubert>{{cite journal |doi=10.1080/07448480009595691 |title=The Longitudinal Effects of a Rape-prevention Program on Fraternity Men's Attitudes, Behavioral Intent, and Behavior |year=2000 |last1=Foubert |first1=John D. |journal=Journal of American College Health |volume=48 |issue=4 |pages=158–63 |pmid=10650733}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1177/1524838010390708 |title=College- or University-Based Sexual Assault Prevention Programs: A Review of Program Outcomes, Characteristics, and Recommendations |year=2010 |last1=Vladutiu |first1=C. J. |last2=Martin |first2=S. L. |last3=Macy |first3=R. J. |journal=Trauma, Violence, & Abuse |volume=12 |issue=2 |pages=67–86 |pmid=21196436}}</ref>、职场<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/S0272-7358(98)00075-0 |title=Sexual assault prevention programs Current issues, future directions, and the potential efficacy of interventions with women |year=1999 |last1=Yeater |first1=E |journal=Clinical Psychology Review |volume=19 |issue=7 |pages=739–71 |pmid=10520434 |last2=O'Donohue |first2=W}}</ref>、教育节目 [http://www.savcalgary.ca/ public] {{Wayback|url=http://www.savcalgary.ca/ |date=20201128085307 }}来进行预防。至少有一些项目为男士联谊会创立“改变行为”<ref name=Foubert /><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1111/j.1939-3938.2010.01094.x |title=Sexual assault prevention programs for college-aged men: A critical evaluation |year=2011 |last1=Garrity |first1=Stacy E. |journal=Journal of Forensic Nursing |volume=7 |pages=40–8 |pmid=21348933 |issue=1}}</ref>。

基于预防强奸的一些研究项目经过科学方式的检验和验证，它们包括：

*男士项目<ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite book |last=Foubert |first=John |title=The Men's and Women's Programs: Ending Rape Through Peer Education |year=2011 |publisher=Routledge |location=New York |isbn=978-0-415-88105-0}}{{page needed|date=November 2013}}</ref>，也被称作一对四项目，由约翰·福伯特写成。它关注了增强对强奸受害人的关心，鼓励男士作为旁观者对强奸进行干预。出版数据显示高危男士参加男士项目后，相对于没有参加项目的男士性强暴行为减少了40%。参加项目的男士在施行性强暴的过程中相对于控制组来说强度减少了8倍<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.2202/1949-6605.1866 |title=Behavior Differences Seven Months Later: Effects of a Rape Prevention Program |year=2008 |last1=Foubert |first1=John D. |last2=Newberry |first2=Johnathan T |last3=Tatum |first3=Jerry |journal=Journal of Student Affairs Research and Practice |volume=44 |issue=4}}</ref>。更多的研究也显示参加男士项目的男士作为旁观者能更加积极主动地干预强奸、帮助受害人<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1177/1077801211409728 |title=The Men's Program: Does It Impact College Men's Self-Reported Bystander Efficacy and Willingness to Intervene? |year=2011 |last1=Langhinrichsen-Rohling |first1=J. |last2=Foubert |first2=J. D. |last3=Brasfield |first3=H. M. |last4=Hill |first4=B. |last5=Shelley-Tremblay |first5=S. |journal=Violence Against Women |volume=17 |issue=6 |pages=743–59 |pmid=21571743}}</ref>其它研究也证实了项目的有效性<ref name = Foubert /><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1177/0886260509354881 |title=In Their Own Words: Sophomore College Men Describe Attitude and Behavior Changes Resulting from a Rape Prevention Program 2 Years After Their Participation |year=2009 |last1=Foubert |first1=J. D. |last2=Godin |first2=E. E. |last3=Tatum |first3=J. L. |journal=Journal of Interpersonal Violence |volume=25 |issue=12 |pages=2237–57 |pmid=20040715}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1007/s11199-007-9216-2 |title=Reactions of Men of Color to a Commonly Used Rape Prevention Program: Attitude and Predicted Behavior Changes |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_sex-roles_2007-07_57_1-2/page/137 |year=2007 |last1=Foubert |first1=John D. |last2=Cremedy |first2=Brandynne J. |journal=Sex Roles |volume=57 |pages=137–44}}</ref>。

*维多利亚·班亚德就加入旁观者撰写了相关资料。它关注的是在危险的境地中旁观者伸出援手的效果。项目包括短暂的同情引导和在未来对干预的恳求。一些研究显示旁观者的干预、帮助受害人可以十分有效地减少强奸问题。<ref>Banyard, Moynihan & Plante, 2007{{full|date=November 2013}}</ref><ref>Banyard, Plante & Moynihan, 2004{{full|date=November 2013}}</ref><ref>Banyard, Ward, Cohn, Plante, Moorhead, & Walsh, 2007{{full|date=November 2013}}</ref>

*绿点项目由桃乐茜·爱德华写成。项目包括旁观者的积极演讲和同龄人教育。结果显示项目参与人在强奸虚构接受程度上有所降低，增加了旁观者干预程度<ref>Coker, Cook-Craig, Williams, Fisher, Clear, Garcia & Hegge, 2011{{full|date=November 2013}}</ref>。

*加拿大卡尔加里市针对潜在的施虐者发起了公共教育运动。酒吧厕所和公交中心都提醒男士“糟蹋她不性感”和“当他改变主意是不是性”。运动十分有效，其它城市也争风效仿。当告示在全城张贴时，温哥华去年所报道的性侵犯数量下降了10%。{{When|这是近年来}}城市性侵犯事件第一次有所下降<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2012/12/01/edmonton-sexual-assault-awareness-campaign-dont-be-that-guy_n_2224228.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-10-01 |archive-date=2017-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171221201343/http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2012/12/01/edmonton-sexual-assault-awareness-campaign-dont-be-that-guy_n_2224228.html |dead-url=yes }}{{full|date=November 2013}}</ref>。

