其它研究关注每年强奸案例，有的研究将比例定为5%。例如，莫勒-郭、道戴尔、高斯和韦施乐(2004)<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=15000502 |year=2004 |last1=Mohler-Kuo |first1=M |last2=Dowdall |first2=GW |last3=Koss |first3=MP |last4=Wechsler |first4=H |title=Correlates of rape while intoxicated in a national sample of college women |volume=65 |issue=1 |pages=37–45 |journal=Journal of studies on alcohol}}</ref>  在对全美25,000名大学女生的研究中发现每学期有4.7%的学生经历过强奸或强奸未遂。研究没有关注她们一生中所经历的强奸或强奸未遂事件。类似地，基尔帕特里克、雷斯尼克、鲁杰罗、康诺森提和麦考利(2007)对全美2,000大学女生的研究中发现有5.2%的人每年会经历强奸事件。<ref>{{cite book |first1=Dean |last1=Kilpatrick |first2=Heidi |last2=Resnick |first3=Kenneth |last3=Ruggiero |first4=Lauren M. |last4=Conoscenti |first5=Jenna |last5=McCauley |title=Drug Facilitated, Incapacitated, and Forcible Rape: A National Study |url=http://www.nsvrc.org/publications/reports/drug-facilitated-incapacitated-and-forcible-rape-national-study |publisher=U.S. Department of Justice |date=July 2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203004356/http://www.nsvrc.org/publications/reports/drug-facilitated-incapacitated-and-forcible-rape-national-study |archivedate=2013年12月3日 |df= }}{{page needed|date=November 2013}}</ref>

